snippet.textDisplay: Super over reaction. I worked in a hospice center where the patients would sometimes have to drink this based on the diet set by their doctor. There was either Nectar thick or Honey Thick. We had Milk, Water, Juice, Coffee. Ive tried it and its not gonna make you gag, the flavor doesn’t change at all. Its the same drink but with the consistency of either Nectar or Honey. However if you put to much in thats another story. I remember a coworker of mine accidentally putting to much in some coffee and creating coffee gravy. The most cursed of gravy which we then spent the next half hour dipping things into (french fries, Fruit, Chips, Ribs) so yea. Its not gross taste wise just odd consistency wise
